('ducato-x250-x290-s8', 'Fiat', 'Ducato', 'X250/X290/Series 8-9', 2006, null, 'Peugeot Boxer / Citroen Relay / Vauxhall Movano (2021+) / Toyota Proace Max', '{3000,3450,4035}', 1810, 1790, 'high', 'very-high', 'Sevel platform; dims unchanged 2006-present across facelifts and all 5 badges. Track per Stellantis official spec sheet, same across L1-L4. Dominant UK/EU camper base.'),
('ducato-244', 'Fiat', 'Ducato', '230/244 (pre-Sevel-X250)', 1994, 2006, 'Peugeot Boxer / Citroen Relay (same era)', '{2850,3200,3700}', 1720, 1720, 'med', 'low', 'Older self-builds only. Track per Ducato II spec (truck1.eu). Wheelbase list TBC - verify before enabling in-app.'),
