('vivaro-c-emp2', 'Vauxhall', 'Vivaro', 'C (Stellantis EMP2)', 2019, null, 'Peugeot Expert / Citroen Dispatch (2016+) / Toyota Proace (2016+) / Fiat Scudo (2022+)', '{2925,3275}', 1627, 1600, 'high', 'med', 'Track per auto-data. Expert/Dispatch/Proace on this platform from 2016; Vivaro joined 2019. Single roof height.'),
